Promise is basically an object and it contains some data ie success response or failure response(What is promise)

3 statesof Promise to determine succes or failure response(Explain promise state)
-pending-If the data is not present in promise object
-fullfilled-success
-rejected-failure

Why promise-because based on respnse we will perform certain operations

If I want to auomate the any task,we have to do using call back function using predefined function then() 
and generally we add 2 then() for failure and other for success


Handling promise object -----
What to do after failure response and What to do after success response 
It can be handled using promise object
